snippet.title: Diana and the Magic Trunk - Diana and Roma dress up for a disco party!
snippet.description:
Diana wants to go to a disco party, but she needs a new dress! The girl sees a Magic Trunk in her room. The Magic Trunk helps Diana choose an outfit for a disco party. Diana and Roma dress up for a disco party!
